(265, 'Toshikazu Kano', 'To whom it may concern,\r\nAsia ...', 'To whom it may concern,\r\nAsia Silk\r\n\r\nMy name is Toshikazu Kano (Mr.) at Kurosu Ind. Co., Ltd., in Hyogo prefecture in Japan. It is the first time for us to write to you, and we are glad to contact you in this occasion.\r\n \r\nWe are a textile manufacturing company, specializing in warp knitting (raschel lace) and dyeing. And we are expanding our business to Dong Van III Industrial Park in Ha Nam province, by setting up dyeing & knitting mills.\r\n \r\nWe came to know you via introduction from Jetro in Hanoi (Japan External Trade Organization), when we were recently researching on the silk yarn manufacturers in northern Vietnam.\r\n \r\nNow, please kindly provide us with any information on the following points;\r\n\r\n1. We are planning to knit your silk yarn into raschel lace by using our knitting machine. So, please inform us of the Unit Price/kg & Yarn Count of your silk yarn. We are especially interested in very thin kinds of silk yarn.\r\n \r\n2. Please note that we are only interested in SILK YARN itself, not silk garments nor any other silk-related products. Appreciate your understanding.\r\n\r\n3. Please send us your company website for our reference, if you have one.\r\n\r\nWe are in a hurry with this matter. Please confirm your receipt of this message by returning an e-mail, and kindly send us your soonest reply.\r\n\r\nThank you for your cooperation.\r\n \r\nBest Regards,\r\n \r\nToshi (Kano, Toshikazu)\r\n \r\n------------------------\r\nKurosu Ind. Co., Ltd.\r\nOversea Business Division\r\n1-17-1, Minami-Mukonosou,\r\nAmagasaki City, Hyogo Prefecture,\r\nJapan (Zip : 661-0033)\r\nTEL : 81-6-6438-0940\r\nFAX : 81-6-6438-8421\r\nE-mail kano@kurosu.info\r\nURL    http://kurosu.info/\r\n--------------------------', '', '81664380940', 'kano@kurosu.info', '', '', 1489372019, 0, '222.147.242.163'),
